</taxonomicName>
sp, 
<emphasis id="B975EAADFF88E72AFE7196A68458FE19" box="[497,622,440,464]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="40">Arundiaria</emphasis>
sp.(?).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C31B6534FF88E72AFF4996C585C7FE3D" box="[201,1009,475,501]" pageId="10" pageNumber="40" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph id="8BBE36BFFF88E72AFF4996C585C7FE3D" blockId="10.[151,1437,151,1184]" box="[201,1009,475,501]" pageId="10" pageNumber="40">
<emphasis id="B975EAADFF88E72AFF4996C5871FFE3D" bold="true" box="[201,297,475,500]" pageId="10" pageNumber="40">Biology.</emphasis>
Living singly or in small groups on stems beneath leaf sheaths.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
